items.title: Hyundai Motor knew India is the future, so ramped up investments, says Chairman
items.description: Hyundai Motor India shares made a weak debut on the exchanges on October 22 after listing at a 1.32 percent discount at Rs 1,934 on the National Stock Exchange against its initial public offer (IPO) price of Rs 1,960.
